Text: Selling Dribble of Cynet Stock Cc I work with Enron Investment Partners and would like to set up an account so that EIP can sell dribble out of its position in Cynet CYNEOB We currently hold preferred stock and intend to convert to common for sale into the public market We intend to begin selling dribble in the middle of March so I would like to set up the administrative end now It is my understanding that I need Your existing templates for setting up a new account These documents include Prime Broker Agreement Corporate Resolution Form W Trading Authorization Authorization to Transfer Funds Please send this information to me as soon as possible Best Claude Tellis Enron Investment Partners

New Account for Selling Dribble Cc Per Theresa Brogans request I am writing to request the existing templates I did receive your message this morning I did not hear from Cheryl but that is OK I would like however to move quickly on setting up this account Let me know a time this afternoon that works for you Best Claude
